The gecode-2.2.0 release located here is not the official version. It is the
official version with a couple of patches (bool-shr.patch and
unqualified-lookup.patch) applied to resolve issues with Gecode 2.2.0 and newer
gcc versions:

http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=526675
https://gcc.gnu.org/gcc-4.7/porting_to.html
